OL,3,CSwinney urged to rule out 'North East
OL,4,Ctax' in SNP manifesto
OL,6,FFirst Minister John Swinney has been
OL,7,Furged to rule out a "North East tax"
OL,8,Fafter documents revealed proposals
OL,9,Fpreviously being considered by the SNP.
OL,11,FAs the SNP prepares to set out its
OL,12,FGeneral Election manifesto on
OL,13,FWednesday, the Scottish Conservatives
OL,14,Fsaid the party must "come clean" about
OL,15,Fplans for a tax on energy businesses
OL,16,Fand changes to non-domestic rates.
