OL,6,FAndrew Bowie, Scottish Tory candidate
OL,7,Ffor West Aberdeenshire and Kincardine,
OL,8,Fsaid any such tax would be "damaging"
OL,9,Ffor businesses in the region.
OL,11,FHe said: "These new documents reveal
OL,12,Fthe SNP were secretly planning a huge
OL,13,Ftax hike on Scottish businesses.
OL,15,F"The SNP's North East tax would have
OL,16,Fput jobs at risk and hammered the
OL,17,Flocal energy sector.
OL,19,F"John Swinney must rule out ever
OL,20,Fintroducing such a damaging new tax.
